(7277, 421, 'privacy_page_privacy_content_2_section_body', ' <p>Your personal information is used to process orders, provide customer support, and send\r\n promotional materials if you have opted in. We do not sell or share your information with\r\n   third parties for marketing purposes.</p>'),
