(7359, 430, 'privacy_page', ''),
(7360, 430, '_privacy_page', 'field_6a01a34ea6337'),
(7361, 430, 'privacy_page_privacy_content_0_section_title', 'Who we are'),
(7362, 430, '_privacy_page_privacy_content_0_section_title', 'field_6a01a39ea633b'),
(7363, 430, 'privacy_page_privacy_content_0_section_body', 'Suggested text: Our website address is: http://example.com.'),
(7364, 430, '_privacy_page_privacy_content_0_section_body', 'field_6a01a3aaa633c'),
(7365, 430, 'privacy_page_privacy_content_1_section_title', 'Comments'),
(7366, 430, '_privacy_page_privacy_content_1_section_title', 'field_6a01a39ea633b'),
(7367, 430, 'privacy_page_privacy_content_1_section_body', ' <p>Suggested text: When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor’s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.</p>\r\n\r\n <p>An anonymized string created from your email address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service privacy policy is  available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.</p>'),
(7368, 430, '_privacy_page_privacy_content_1_section_body', 'field_6a01a3aaa633c'),
(7369, 430, 'privacy_page_privacy_content_2_section_title', 'Media'),
(7370, 430, '_privacy_page_privacy_content_2_section_title', 'field_6a01a39ea633b'),
(7371, 430, 'privacy_page_privacy_content_2_section_body', ' <p>Your personal information is used to process orders, provide customer support, and send\r\n promotional materials if you have opted in. We do not sell or share your information with\r\n   third parties for marketing purposes.</p>'),
(7372, 430, '_privacy_page_privacy_content_2_section_body', 'field_6a01a3aaa633c'),
(7373, 430, 'privacy_page_privacy_content_3_section_title', 'Data Security'),
(7374, 430, '_privacy_page_privacy_content_3_section_title', 'field_6a01a39ea633b'),
(7375, 430, 'privacy_page_privacy_content_3_section_body', '  <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized  access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the  internet is completely secure, so we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>\r\n  <p>Suggested text: If you leave a comment on our site you may opt-in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.</p>\r\n <p>If you visit our login page, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser  accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your  browser.</p>\r\n <p>When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select \"Remember Me\", your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out  of your account, the login cookies will be removed.</p>\r\n  <p>If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This   cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just\r\n'),
(7376, 430, '_privacy_page_privacy_content_3_section_body', 'field_6a01a3aaa633c'),
(7377, 430, 'privacy_page_privacy_content_4_section_title', 'Cookies'),
(7378, 430, '_privacy_page_privacy_content_4_section_title', 'field_6a01a39ea633b'),
(7379, 430, 'privacy_page_privacy_content_4_section_body', ' <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. You can also opt out of receiving marketing communications at any time by following the unsubscribe link in our emails.</p>'),
(7380, 430, '_privacy_page_privacy_content_4_section_body', 'field_6a01a3aaa633c'),
(7381, 430, 'privacy_page_privacy_content_5_section_title', 'Embedded content from other website'),
(7382, 430, '_privacy_page_privacy_content_5_section_title', 'field_6a01a39ea633b'),
(7383, 430, 'privacy_page_privacy_content_5_section_body', ' <p>Suggested text: Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images,\r\n  articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if\r\n   the visitor has visited the other website.</p>\r\n    <p>These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party\r\n    tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that\r\n   websites.</p>'),
(7384, 430, '_privacy_page_privacy_content_5_section_body', 'field_6a01a3aaa633c'),
(7385, 430, 'privacy_page_privacy_content_6_section_title', 'Changes to This Privacy Polic'),
(7386, 430, '_privacy_page_privacy_content_6_section_title', 'field_6a01a39ea633b'),
(7387, 430, 'privacy_page_privacy_content_6_section_body', '<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page  with an updated effective date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay  informed about how we are protecting your information.</p>'),
(7388, 430, '_privacy_page_privacy_content_6_section_body', 'field_6a01a3aaa633c'),
(7389, 430, 'privacy_page_newsletter_sec_news_title', 'Subscribe To Our Newsletter'),
(7390, 430, '_privacy_page_newsletter_sec_news_title', 'field_6a01a9c5bc9a5'),
(7391, 430, 'privacy_page_newsletter_sec_news_desc', 'Subscribe to our latest newsletter to get news about special discounts.'),
(7392, 430, '_privacy_page_newsletter_sec_news_desc', 'field_6a01a9d8bc9a6'),
(7393, 430, 'privacy_page_newsletter_sec_news_bg_img', '307'),
(7394, 430, '_privacy_page_newsletter_sec_news_bg_img', 'field_6a01a9debc9a7'),
